                <div>
                
        <div class="border-t-0 border-gray-300 pb-3 text-opecgray">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mt-4"></h3>
            <div class="p-0 m-0 text-lg lg:text-base text-opecgray text-justify">
                <div>Space exploration stands among humanity’s most remarkable achievements, powered in part by a wide range of petroleum-based products. From rocket fuels that enable liftoff to advanced materials used in spacecraft and protective gear, oil-derived components are embedded in every mission. They help ensure performance, protection, and safe return to Earth.&nbsp;</div><div>These everyday applications reflect OPEC’s ongoing analysis of how petroleum products continue to support innovation and modern life.</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                            </div>
        </div>
    


